== 個人生活 ==
亞倫·哈利洛維奇的父親{{link-en|塞亞德·哈利洛維奇|Sejad Halilović}}也是一位曾經效力於[[萨格勒布迪纳摩足球俱乐部|薩格勒布迪納摩]]的足球員，同時亦曾代表[[克羅地亞國家足球隊|克羅地亞]]與[[波士尼亞與赫塞哥維納國家足球隊|波黑]]出賽<ref name="Allen Halilović's family">{{Cite web |url=http://www.totalbarca.com/2014/news/two-in-one-after-alen-dino-also-signs |title=Two in one: After Alen, Dino also signs |accessdate=2015-05-10 |archive-date=2015-02-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150201221243/http://www.totalbarca.com/2014/news/two-in-one-after-alen-dino-also-signs/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。在亞倫與其弟弟迪諾（Dino）、達米爾（Damir）一起與巴塞簽約後，他們舉家搬遷至[[巴塞羅那|巴塞羅那]]<ref name="Allen Halilović's family" />。他亦是[[塞拉耶佛足球俱樂部|塞拉耶佛足球俱樂部]]的支持者<ref name=alenhalilovic>{{cite web|url=http://www.klix.ba/sport/nogomet/alen-halilovic-uvijek-sam-navijao-za-sarajevo-reci-cu-i-messiju/140808027|title=Alen Halilović: Uvijek sam navijao za Sarajevo, reći ću i Messiju|language=bs|publisher=''Klix.ba''|accessdate=17 March 2015|archive-date=2019-06-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190629095445/https://www.klix.ba/sport/nogomet/alen-halilovic-uvijek-sam-navijao-za-sarajevo-reci-cu-i-messiju/140808027|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

